    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride that still has tons of life left? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and runs like a dream. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of love from the road, but it\u2019s been well-maintained and is totally ready for its next big adventure. You\u2019re going to love how it handles! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
