    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, the engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to deliver a linear 333 hp power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, feeding power to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the communicative steering and 50/50 weight distribution this platform is renowned for. A performance-oriented driver with excellent mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
